No, it...

00:38:51.640 --> 00:38:54.750
It's out. The head is out!

00:38:54.750 --> 00:38:57.600
- The baby's head?
- Yes.

00:38:57.600 --> 00:39:00.090
- The baby's head is out!
- Okay.

00:39:00.090 --> 00:39:01.930
The baby's head is out.

00:39:01.930 --> 00:39:02.970
Niijima-san.

