Listen and do not panic.

00:39:22.240 --> 00:39:24.310
We'll deliver the baby in the vehicle.

00:39:24.310 --> 00:39:26.210
- What? Here?
- Yes.

00:39:26.210 --> 00:39:28.240
If the baby's head is already out,

00:39:28.240 --> 00:39:31.410
we have to get it breathing before arriving at the ambulance.

00:39:31.410 --> 00:39:33.650
No, but...

00:39:33.650 --> 00:39:35.750
I will drive as fast and carefully as possible.

00:39:35.750 --> 00:39:37.640
Do your best!

00:39:38.740 --> 00:39:40.510
You may keep me on the line.

00:39:40.510 --> 00:39:41.960
Let's do our best together!

00:39:41.960 --> 00:39:43.640
Okay. I'd appreciate any assistance.

00:39:43.640 --> 00:39:45.140
Right.

00:39:47.540 --> 00:39:50.310
- Contact her OB-GYN doctor as well.
- Copy that.

