Please park the taxi behind the ambulance.

00:42:42.580 --> 00:42:44.210
The paramedics will handle the rest.

00:42:44.210 --> 00:42:46.640
Thank you. Thank you!

00:42:46.640 --> 00:42:50.430
Thank you for cooperating.

00:42:50.430 --> 00:42:53.980
And congratulations on your healthy baby.

00:42:53.980 --> 00:42:56.200
Thank you.

